{"type": "article", "id": 48094, "title": "节日季，也给毛茸茸小朋友们一点礼物吧｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-12-08T23:11:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 37258, "name": "宠物用品"}, {"id": 46186, "name": "HOWL + HOUND"}, {"id": 46187, "name": "Isle of Dogs"}, {"id": 46188, "name": "West Paw"}, {"id": 46189, "name": "Bad Marlon"}, {"id": 46190, "name": "Square Cat Habitat"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171208200424KfdEABsZFQLUuCeb.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>囤狗粮，买猫砂，看着那些猫猫狗狗的主人，会觉得有些人对待自己的小宠物，用心程度和父母对待自己的人类幼仔没什么区别。</p><p>当然，狗粮猫砂之类，已经算是最基础的需求了。在享受宠物的陪伴，且接受了这份无暇而真诚的情感后，人们对待宠物友好的方式也越来越多样化。这个周末，我们一起来看看，设计师们是如何满足宠物们更高级的需求（当然可能也只是人类的一厢情愿）。</p><h3>Wall-Mounted Cat Perches from Square Cat Habitat </h3><p>家里的地面空间对于猫来说永远是不够玩的。它们总喜欢跳上跳下，带着一种审视的姿态摸清家中的每一寸空间。</p><p>主营现代斯堪的纳维亚式猫家具的品牌 Square Cat Habitat 推出的这款猫咪搁架，可以轻松地安装在家里的任何墙壁上、窗台下，或者你认为合适的墙壁空间，它允许猫咪在上面进食饮水，也可以休息玩乐，提供高达约 23 斤的重量支持，可选的饰面和颜色也很多，能够匹配不同家庭的家装风格。售价 75 美元，<a href=\"https://www.squarecathabitat.com/burnside-perch.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017120820052162s9rcOoSgYpGFl4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200521KcF8HkMU6ToXQC2m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.852500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200521TboM4da7fY35ghjW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.936000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200522DzWPQI2JtGMglFL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200521qYHvafyz7egmZBoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.427023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Marron Bed from Bad Marlon</h3><p>这款 Marron 床是韩国设计团队 Bad Marlon 的新作，他们此前就曾为小型的汪星人或喵星人设计过宠物小屋。这次的 Marron 床由柔软而坚韧的毛毡制作而成，使用 100% 黄铜螺栓组装，便于拆卸和清洁。内置一块柔软、蓬松的超细纤维坐垫，希望能够给狗狗带去安全感。海军蓝和燕麦白的色调很高级，售价 132 美元，<a href=\"https://www.badmarlon.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200612Dkpg6l2EIJw1C9ov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200612SNTkIjaehD0u7P92.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712082006124bQgVG6q7IJBAR0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200612BYXCz9aWl7mNuTKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666797\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200612GDToAtucvsSmq5Fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200614SqYufnVabiTLsjK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dash Dog Frisbee from West Paw</h3><p>West Paw 是美国知名的宠物用品品牌，这款 Dash 飞盘可抛接，可浮水，是和狗狗互动的理想玩具。相较于之前的实心飞盘，中心孔的设计允许飞盘更平稳快速地飞行和下降，耐用的外壳包裹着软质泡沫材料，不会伤到狗狗的嘴巴和人的手。它不含乳胶、BPA 等，保证用料安全，对狗狗无毒无害。售价 17.95 美元，<a href=\"https://www.westpaw.com/toys/dog-toys/zogoflex-air-dog-toys/dash-dog-frisbee\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200651TpmjnfSXrO1PG5Ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200651bohGA6OFmXr0l7C9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200651gqG5h1xecCSPatdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200651A2K0t7dUwyurxEYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Calming Collection by Isle of Dogs</h3><p>狗狗抑郁、焦虑了怎么办？这是美国宠物用品品牌 Isle of Dogs 推出的抗焦虑镇静系列产品，包括一款营养益生菌、一瓶镇定洗发水、一把镇定毛发刷以及一袋 100% 天然烤面包和小狗零食。你的狗狗可能需要一些独处的时间。如果它们被过度刺激，请让它们在一个令其感觉安全的空间里有一些安静的时间，平静地享受吃小食的时光，或是给它洗个澡，用毛发刷轻轻为它理一理毛。售价 8.99—29.99 美元不等，<a href=\"https://iodogs.com/collections/anti-anxiety-calming\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726iFRKBUWI3lhdDerP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726S3MjRap2WhL0iA7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726fUksFrD8u57jTZ3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726G8DqElOYoiBkMTL6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726ODhM6o3kXHeTyfsW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200726VZ8yPrHtWfJI1aMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Holiday Bandana Collection from HOWL + HOUND</h3><p>圣诞新年临近，各种派对需要出席，狗狗也需要装扮一番，很可能就会成为了宴会上明星宠物。</p><p>位于纽约布鲁克林的时尚狗狗宠物品牌 HOWL + HOUND 推出的这一系列头巾，不失为一种既便利又时髦的选择。你不必费心为狗狗做发型，选衣服，各种不同风格的头巾就能创造出特别的形象。每款头巾都有 6 种尺寸可供选择，以适应各种体型的狗，且提供传统款或搭扣式两种选择。售价 14 美元，<a href=\"https://www.shophowlandhound.com/new-arrivals\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200758RdgYOGTq51pEAWaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200758NsnhiRmrkMJvLAx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712082007584OPceyEqVwAaY07m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200759qicDpGL4Y2uEC5H1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200759GCWzUk2eorFXynmJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pebby by Team Pebby</h3><p>各位猫奴狗友们，你们肯定很好奇外出时猫猫狗狗们在家都做些什么，一款名为 Pebby 的智能宠物波，可以帮助你和宠物们远程互动。</p><p>Debby 的外壳采用 Rimowa 行李箱使用的防弹塑料，耐磨且防水，不怕猫抓和狗咬。人们可以通过 App 远程遥控球体，和猫狗们互动。特别的是，Pebby 还可以自动回到插电座充电。此外，它还设有广角镜头，记录宠物们玩耍时的有爱瞬间，而且人们还可以透过麦克风，与猫狗们进行对话。售价 189 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/pebby-world-s-most-advanced-smart-ball-for-pets#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208201112SHDG6hdANEmrio7p.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551440\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208201117UEJWsRu2FTN4i8zp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552174\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208201118r3dkxUuDSY9O5aNM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200830xJ3BFrfWtsoUzlj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200830aY9tVDwWo2dBuXMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171208200831cQgJio6xp9MB1yrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.802941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}